MobileCashLedgerPaymentCardView is a CardView
    show labels
    main column
        CashLedgerTransactionIdentifier
        CashCode
        CashLedgerPayment.BankTransactionCode
        TransactionNumber
            label is "PaymentNumber"
        BankCheckAmount
            raise red alert when (OutOfBalance)
                mouse over text is "PaymentOutOfBalanceBy:<BalanceAmount>"
        Status
        PaymentDate
